      ],
      "source": "https://www.cityneighborhoods.nyc/bayside"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Founded in 1964, the Bayside Historical Society preserves the town’s heritage and hosts guided tours of Lawrence Cemetery, sometimes featuring theatrical reenactments.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        1,
        4,
        13
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
